I"5<p>I gave a contributed talk at the <a href="http://web.miaapt.org/meetings/fall-2016">Fall 2016 Michigan AAPT meeting</a> on integrating computation across the curriculum. Here’s the talk: <a href="https://github.com/dannycab/dannycab.github.io/blob/master/assets/docs/2016_MIAAPT.pdf">Supporting the integration of computation into physics courses</a>.</p>

